    <section class="section bg-white border-bottom" style="padding-top: 0;">
        <div class="container">
            
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>Yevro Polycarbonate provides written warranty documentation for eligible polycarbonate sheets supplied in Canada. Our warranties are strictly <strong>UV Performance warranties</strong> (not general “everything” warranties) and apply only when products are stored, handled, installed, and maintained correctly.</p>
                <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy);">If you need the written warranty documents for a project submittal, download them below:</p>
            </div>

            <div class="warranty-grid">
                
                <div class="warranty-card">
                    <div class="warranty-badge">10 Years</div>
                    <h2>Multiwall Polycarbonate</h2>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">Eligible Yevro-supplied multiwall polycarbonate sheets include a written 10-year UV Performance warranty.</p>
                    
                    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--navy);">Key conditions for coverage:</strong>
                    <ul class="condition-list">
                        <li>Store sheets properly prior to installation (flat, supported, protected from heat build-up and weather exposure)</li>
                        <li>Install correctly and allow for natural thermal expansion/contraction</li>
                        <li>Install the UV-protected side facing outward (where applicable)</li>
                        <li>Use compatible tapes, sealants, and cleaners</li>
                        <li>Follow proper end-closure practices for multiwall flutes</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <a href="assets/multiwall-warranty.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-download">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-pdf" style="color: #ef4444;"></i> Download UV Warranty (PDF)
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="warranty-card">
                    <div class="warranty-badge" style="background: #fce7f3; color: #be185d;">15 Years</div>
                    <h2>Solid Polycarbonate</h2>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">Eligible Yevro-supplied solid polycarbonate sheets include a written 15-year UV Performance warranty.</p>
                    
                    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--navy);">Key conditions for coverage:</strong>
                    <ul class="condition-list">
                        <li>Store sheets properly prior to installation (flat, supported, protected from heat build-up and weather exposure)</li>
                        <li>Install correctly and allow for natural thermal expansion/contraction</li>
                        <li>Use compatible sealants and cleaners (strictly avoid harsh solvents)</li>
                        <li>Avoid exposure to incompatible chemicals and fumes</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <a href="assets/solid-warranty.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-download">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-pdf" style="color: #ef4444;"></i> Download UV Warranty (PDF)
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="important-notes">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Important Notes (Please Read)</h3>
                <p>These are UV Performance warranties only. They do not cover physical damage, scratches, impact damage, chemical damage from incompatible products, or issues caused by incorrect storage, handling, fabrication, or installation.</p>
                <p>Labor, removal/re-installation, project delays, and consequential damages are not covered, except where required by law.</p>
                <p><strong>Warranty eligibility and remedies are governed strictly by the written warranty terms in the downloadable PDF documents.</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-claims">
                <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">Warranty Questions or Claims</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 20px;">If you have a warranty question or need to start a claim, contact us with your invoice number, product details, and photos of the issue.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 5px;"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:akhmed@yevropolycarbonate.ca" style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;">akhmed@yevropolycarbonate.ca</a></p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+14038797209" style="color: var(--navy); font-weight: 700;">(403) 879-7209</a></p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

